level-up.name: splash
level-up.description:
The user just flops and splashes around to no effect
at all...
level-up.effect:
Does nothing.

This move cannot be used while gravity is in effect.

level-up.name: teleport
level-up.description:
The user switches places with a party Pokémon in
waiting, if any. If a wild Pokémon uses this move,
it flees.
level-up.effect: Does nothing.  Wild battles end immediately.
